WEBVTT

00:02.769 --> 00:06.205
GIVE ME 30 cc OF FENTANYL,
STRAT!

00:06.207 --> 00:08.640
[ PLAYS CHORD ]

00:08.642 --> 00:13.545
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:14.547 --> 00:16.482
-SORE THROAT, HUH?
-MM-HMM.

00:16.484 --> 00:18.550
-THOSE HAVE BEEN GOING AROUND.
-HMM.

00:18.552 --> 00:19.885
THROATS, I MEAN.

00:19.887 --> 00:21.353
JUST ABOUT EVERYBODY'S GOT ONE
OF THOSE.

00:21.355 --> 00:22.388
LET ME TAKE A LOOK WITH

00:22.390 --> 00:23.489
THE OLD TONGUE DEPRESSOR.

00:23.491 --> 00:25.224
OH.

00:25.226 --> 00:28.360
GIVE ME JUST A SECOND.

00:28.362 --> 00:32.197
♪♪

00:37.737 --> 00:39.238
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]
OH, HEY, CHIEF.

00:39.240 --> 00:41.273
DO YOU KNOW WHERE I CAN FIND
A TONGUE DEPRESSOR?

00:41.275 --> 00:43.475
♪♪

00:43.477 --> 00:44.543
SURE.

00:44.545 --> 00:46.145
I'LL HELP YOU LOOK

00:46.147 --> 00:48.013
FOR A "TONG DEPRESSOR."

00:48.015 --> 00:50.649
♪♪

00:50.651 --> 00:52.484
NOPE, NO "TONG DEPRESSORS."

00:52.486 --> 00:54.186
BUT YOU DIDN'T REALLY LOOK --

00:54.188 --> 00:55.921
CAN'T HELP YOU!

01:00.160 --> 01:03.195
Owen:
TONGUE BAGS, TONGUE CANDLES,

01:03.197 --> 01:04.897
TONGUE EXTENDERS.

01:04.899 --> 01:08.300
WHERE THE HELL
ARE THE TONGUE DEPRESSORS?

01:08.302 --> 01:09.868
-BLAKE.
-HEY, OWEN.

01:09.870 --> 01:11.303
I NEED TO FIND
A TONGUE DEPRESSOR.

01:11.305 --> 01:12.404
I CAN'T FIND ONE ANYWHERE.

01:12.406 --> 01:14.139
♪♪

01:14.141 --> 01:17.009
HI.

01:17.011 --> 01:18.811
WHY ARE YOU POKING
THE HORNET'S NEST, BROTHER?

01:18.813 --> 01:22.481
HORNETS DON'T LIKE HAVING
THEIR NESTS POKED AT.

01:22.483 --> 01:24.950
LEAVE IT ALONE.

01:24.952 --> 01:27.953
♪♪

01:27.955 --> 01:30.956
WELL, IF NO ONE'S GONNA HELP ME
FIND A TONGUE DEPRESSOR,

01:30.958 --> 01:33.192
I GUESS I'LL JUST HAVE TO DO IT
MYSELF.

01:33.194 --> 01:34.560
HEY, SPREAD THE WORD.

01:34.562 --> 01:36.562
I THINK THE HOSPITAL
MAY HAVE A HORNET PROBLEM.

01:36.564 --> 01:40.299
[ KEYBOARD CLICKING ]

01:40.301 --> 01:43.335
♪♪

01:43.337 --> 01:47.106
WHAT THE HELL...

01:47.108 --> 01:49.541
IS GOING ON?

01:49.543 --> 01:52.277
OKAY, LET ME JUST PUSH
YOUR TONGUE DOWN.

01:52.279 --> 01:53.445
HEY, GLENN, DO YOU KNOW --

01:53.447 --> 01:54.780
YOU, TOO?

01:54.782 --> 01:56.281
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH THE TONGUE DEPRESSORS?

01:56.283 --> 01:57.382
I WENT ONLINE AND I --

01:57.384 --> 01:58.650
TONGUE DEPRESSORS?

01:58.652 --> 02:00.819
WHAT'S A TONGUE DEPRESSOR?

02:00.821 --> 02:02.921
THIS IS HOW I'VE ALWAYS DONE IT.

02:02.923 --> 02:06.458
[ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYS ]

02:06.460 --> 02:07.860
Glenn: OKAY. DOWN.

02:07.862 --> 02:11.230
[ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYS ]

02:17.270 --> 02:19.271
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

02:19.273 --> 02:20.906
WHO GAVE THIS TO YOU?

02:24.477 --> 02:27.346
AAH!

02:27.348 --> 02:31.917
[ INDISTINCT WHISPERING ]

02:37.757 --> 02:40.359
[ WHISPERING CONTINUES ]

02:46.232 --> 02:47.232
HEY, OWEN!

02:47.234 --> 02:48.767
WHAT'S HAPPENING?
IS IT THE HORNETS?

02:48.769 --> 02:50.335
NO, YOUR PATIENT JUST WOKE UP
FROM HIS COMA.

02:50.337 --> 02:52.938
GO, GO, GO!

02:52.940 --> 02:55.374
WELCOME BACK, BRADEN.

02:55.376 --> 02:57.676
YOU'VE BEEN UNCONSCIOUS
A LONG TIME, BUDDY.

02:57.678 --> 02:59.912
LET'S TAKE A LOOK AT YOU.

03:01.781 --> 03:03.115
SAY "AAH."

03:03.117 --> 03:06.251
WHY AREN'T YOU USING
A TONGUE DEPRESSOR?

03:06.253 --> 03:07.753
[ Softly ]
You know what that is?

03:07.755 --> 03:09.955
EVERYONE KNOWS WHAT
A TONGUE DEPRESSOR IS.

03:09.957 --> 03:11.523
YOUR FINGER TASTES
LIKE A DOG TRACK.

03:11.525 --> 03:13.525
STAY RIGHT HERE.

03:13.527 --> 03:15.427
HEY, HEY,

03:15.429 --> 03:17.796
TONGUE DEPRESSORS ARE REAL,
AND I CAN PROVE IT.

03:17.798 --> 03:20.499
COME ON, MAN.
STOP TALKING CRAZY.

03:20.501 --> 03:21.833
LISTEN TO BRADEN.
HE REMEMBERS.

03:21.835 --> 03:23.368
[ MONITOR FLATLINES ]
Glenn: OH, GOD.

03:23.370 --> 03:24.436
Owen: NO!

03:24.438 --> 03:25.604
NO, NO, NO.

03:25.606 --> 03:26.905
HE WAS THE ONLY ONE
WHO KNEW.

03:26.907 --> 03:28.106
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

03:28.108 --> 03:28.907
WHAT?

03:28.909 --> 03:30.075
I DIDN'T DO THIS?

03:30.077 --> 03:31.743
ARREST THIS MAN
FOR MURDER.

03:31.745 --> 03:33.712
NO!
HOW DID THEY GET HERE SO FAST?

03:33.714 --> 03:36.081
GLENN, I DIDN'T DO IT.

03:36.083 --> 03:38.083
IT'S A SETUP.
I'M A PATSY.

03:38.085 --> 03:39.618
GLENN!

03:39.620 --> 03:43.355
[ EERIE MUSIC PLAYS ]

03:43.357 --> 03:45.324
[ SNEEZES ]

03:45.326 --> 03:47.559
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

03:47.561 --> 03:50.796
[ GRUNTING ]

03:50.798 --> 03:52.564
I WANT MY LAWYER!

03:52.566 --> 03:53.632
[ DOOR OPENS ]

03:53.634 --> 03:56.735
WELL, WELL, WELL.

03:56.737 --> 04:00.706
GOVERNOR JASPER RUTH,
THE BOSS TWEED OF SAO PAOLO,

04:00.708 --> 04:02.341
WHICH AS WE ALL KNOW
IS WHERE --

04:02.343 --> 04:04.476
I HEAR YOU'VE BEEN
A BAD BOY TODAY.

04:04.478 --> 04:06.478
STABBING A CHILD?

04:06.480 --> 04:07.613
TSK, TSK, TSK.

04:07.615 --> 04:08.680
I'M A DOCTOR, RUTH.

04:08.682 --> 04:10.449
I ONLY KILL CHILDREN
BY ACCIDENT.

04:10.451 --> 04:11.783
YOU KNOW, I'D HATE TO SEE

04:11.785 --> 04:13.952
SUCH A PROMISING CAREER
END LIKE THIS.

04:13.954 --> 04:17.255
IF YOU JUST ADMIT TO MAKING UP
ALL THIS NONSENSE

04:17.257 --> 04:20.158
ABOUT TONGUE DEPRESSORS,
I MIGHT BE ABLE

04:20.160 --> 04:22.461
TO MAKE
ALL THIS GO AWAY.

04:22.463 --> 04:24.630
WAIT A SECOND.

04:24.632 --> 04:25.964
YOU'RE BEHIND ALL THIS?

04:25.966 --> 04:28.467
LOOK AT YOU,
PUTTING IT ALL TOGETHER

04:28.469 --> 04:31.937
JUST LIKE MY CHILD
PUTS TOGETHER MODEL BRIDGES.

04:31.939 --> 04:33.805
YOU CAN'T SILENCE ME,

04:33.807 --> 04:36.108
AND THAT'S THE TRUTH,
GOVERNOR RUTH.

04:36.110 --> 04:38.677
I HOPE YOU
HAVE A GOOD LAWYER.

04:38.679 --> 04:41.980
[ DOOR OPENS ]

04:41.982 --> 04:44.349
WORD IN THIS DOORWAY IS
YOU NEED A GOOD LAWYER.

04:44.351 --> 04:45.817
LOLA.

04:45.819 --> 04:47.519
OH, THANK GOD.

04:47.521 --> 04:49.321
WAIT. YOU'RE A LAWYER?

04:49.323 --> 04:50.222
I'M A LOT OF THINGS.

04:50.224 --> 04:51.923
WE GOT TO GET YOU
OUT OF HERE.

04:51.925 --> 04:56.295
WAIT.
WHERE'D YOU GET THOSE KEYS?

04:56.297 --> 04:57.963
MY BRA.

04:57.965 --> 04:58.964
WHY ARE YOU HELPING ME?

04:58.966 --> 05:00.332
I DIDN'T HELP YOU.

05:00.334 --> 05:04.303
YOU OVERPOWERED ME,
AND THEN YOU TOOK MY GUN.

05:04.305 --> 05:05.604
YOU HAVE A GUN, TOO?

05:05.606 --> 05:07.072
AND I HAVE THIS.

05:07.074 --> 05:08.940
A TONGUE DEPRESSOR.

05:08.942 --> 05:10.142
IT WILL HELP YOU
FIND THE TRUTH

05:10.144 --> 05:12.144
WHEN YOU'RE READY TO HEAR IT.

05:12.146 --> 05:12.944
NOW RUN.

05:12.946 --> 05:14.246
LOLA, I OWE YOU --

05:14.248 --> 05:15.514
NO, RUN!

05:15.516 --> 05:17.849
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

05:17.851 --> 05:18.917
[ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYS ]

05:18.919 --> 05:20.218
CAN'T TRUST ANYONE.

05:20.220 --> 05:22.554
GOT TO STICK TO THE SHADOWS.

05:22.556 --> 05:25.957
♪♪

05:31.364 --> 05:35.400
[ POLICE SIREN WAILS ]

05:53.853 --> 05:57.189
MMM, MMM!

05:57.924 --> 05:59.157
[ GROANS ]

05:59.159 --> 06:01.460
WHO SERVES RED ZINFANDEL
WITH TILAPIA?

06:01.462 --> 06:03.228
I CAN'T DO THIS ANYMORE.

06:03.230 --> 06:04.830
[ SIGHS ]

06:04.832 --> 06:07.766
I'M READY TO KNOW THE TRUTH.

06:07.768 --> 06:11.503
♪♪

06:11.505 --> 06:13.572
[ CLEARS THROAT, GAGS ]

06:13.574 --> 06:14.940
HELLO?

06:14.942 --> 06:16.808
WHO'S THERE?

06:16.810 --> 06:19.978
[ Hoarse voice ]
WHO I AM IS NOT IMPORTANT.

06:19.980 --> 06:21.646
OH, HEY, LOLA.

06:21.648 --> 06:23.648
WHAT?
I'M NOT LOLA. NO.

06:23.650 --> 06:25.250
YOU JUST STEPPED INTO
A BIG PATCH OF LIGHT,

06:25.252 --> 06:26.818
SO I CAN SEE THAT IT'S YOU.

06:26.820 --> 06:28.987
WHAT?
OH, UH --

06:28.989 --> 06:31.690
OKAY, UM --

06:31.692 --> 06:33.692
HOW'S THIS?

06:33.694 --> 06:34.960
IT'S FINE.
LOLA, PLEASE.

06:34.962 --> 06:37.095
I'VE BEEN ON THE RUN
FOR ABOUT TWO HOURS.

06:37.097 --> 06:38.797
ASK YOURSELF THIS QUESTION.

06:38.799 --> 06:41.800
WHY WOULD GOVERNOR RUTH
WANT TO ERASE

06:41.802 --> 06:43.902
TONGUE DEPRESSORS FROM
EXISTENCE?

06:43.904 --> 06:45.370
I DON'T KNOW.

06:45.372 --> 06:46.571
YOU DO!

06:46.573 --> 06:48.173
HE TOLD YOU.

06:48.175 --> 06:51.676
GO BACK TO WHERE
IT ALL BEGAN.

06:51.678 --> 06:53.945
ANCIENT MESOPOTAMIA.

06:53.947 --> 06:55.113
OF COURSE.

06:55.115 --> 06:57.048
NO, NOT MES--
NO, DON'T GO THERE!

06:57.050 --> 06:59.518
JUST GO BACK
TO THE HOSPITAL.

06:59.520 --> 07:01.920
THE HOSPITAL.
THAT MAKES A LOT MORE SENSE.

07:01.922 --> 07:03.555
THANKS, LOLA.

07:03.557 --> 07:05.857
YOU'RE WELCOME.
BUT, UH, I'M NOT LOLA!

07:05.859 --> 07:09.027
UH, I MEAN, BUT I --
BUT I KNOW HER.

07:09.029 --> 07:10.796
SHE'S A GOOD KID.

07:10.798 --> 07:15.233
OKAY, "REFUSE TO GIVE NAME,"

07:15.235 --> 07:17.102
WHAT SEEMS TO BE THE PROBLEM
TODAY?

07:17.104 --> 07:19.471
MY TONGUE'S DEPRESSED.

07:19.473 --> 07:22.340
MM, YEAH, I'VE BEEN SEEING
A LOT OF THAT LATELY.

07:22.342 --> 07:25.210
♪♪

07:25.212 --> 07:26.445
OWEN!

07:26.447 --> 07:27.612
IT'S ME. OWEN.

07:27.614 --> 07:29.114
[ Whispering ]
It's not safe for you here.

07:29.116 --> 07:31.583
[ Loudly ]
SO, UH, YOUR TONGUE IS SAD, HUH?

07:31.585 --> 07:32.818
WELL, LET'S TAKE A LOOK.

07:32.820 --> 07:34.486
I DIDN'T KILL THAT PATIENT.

07:34.488 --> 07:35.754
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T.

07:35.756 --> 07:38.824
YOU WANT THE TRUTH?

07:38.826 --> 07:41.560
I CAN TAKE YOU TO IT.

07:41.562 --> 07:43.829
HERE'S YOUR TRUTH.

07:43.831 --> 07:45.597
THANK YOU, DR. DOWNS.

07:45.599 --> 07:46.865
WHAT?

07:46.867 --> 07:50.335
GET OFF ME, YOU BALD, BEARD,
TRACK SUIT --

07:50.337 --> 07:51.470
[ GROANS ]

07:51.472 --> 07:54.306
BLAKE.
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

07:54.308 --> 07:56.908
'CAUSE YOU ASK TOO MANY
QUESTIONS, OWEN.

07:56.910 --> 07:58.343
I'M DISAPPOINTED
IN YOU, SON.

07:58.345 --> 08:00.078
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
SMARTER THAN THIS.

08:00.080 --> 08:03.315
TIME TO OPERATE, BOYS.

08:03.317 --> 08:05.317
AAH!
THROAT GRAB!

08:05.319 --> 08:06.451
HEAD SLAM!

08:06.453 --> 08:08.286
UGH!                        UGH!

08:08.288 --> 08:10.088
GUN PULL.

08:10.090 --> 08:14.025
COME ON, MAN.
THEY PAID ME A LOT OF MONEY.

08:14.027 --> 08:15.694
[ PANTING ]
DON'T DO IT.

08:15.696 --> 08:17.863
DON'T TAKE ANOTHER STEP.
I'LL SHOOT HIM, I SWEAR.

08:17.865 --> 08:19.397
NO, PLEASE,
DON'T KILL THE CLOWN.

08:19.399 --> 08:20.765
WE LOVE HIM.

08:20.767 --> 08:22.534
[ LAUGHS ]
IT'S SO HARD

08:22.536 --> 08:25.003
TO SAY THAT
WITHOUT LAUGHING.

08:25.005 --> 08:26.538
NOBODY CARES.

08:26.540 --> 08:27.639
IT'S OVER, SON.

08:27.641 --> 08:28.640
NO, IT'S NOT.

08:28.642 --> 08:30.375
OWEN DIDN'T KILL BRADEN.

08:30.377 --> 08:32.177
WELL, THEN WHO DID?
Please say the clown.

08:32.179 --> 08:34.846
NO.
THE PERSON BEHIND BRADEN'S DEATH

08:34.847 --> 08:39.351
IS THE SAME PERSON
BEHIND THIS ENTIRE CONSPIRACY.

08:39.352 --> 08:41.419
MY FATHER.

08:41.421 --> 08:42.320
LOLA, DARLING.

08:42.322 --> 08:44.121
GOVERNOR RUTH
IS YOUR FATHER?

08:44.124 --> 08:45.757
IT ALL STARTED LAST TUESDAY

08:45.759 --> 08:48.793
WHEN THE WEEKLY SHIPMENT OF
TONGUE DEPRESSORS ARRIVED.

08:48.795 --> 08:50.962
♪♪

08:50.964 --> 08:52.163
IT WAS JUST WHAT I NEEDED

08:52.165 --> 08:53.431
TO FINISH MY MODEL
SUSPENSION BRIDGE

08:53.433 --> 08:55.734
I'VE BEEN WORKING ON
IN MY SPARE TIME.

08:55.736 --> 08:59.704
<i>...JUST LIKE MY CHILD</i>
<i>PUTS TOGETHER MODEL BRIDGES.</i>

08:59.706 --> 09:02.140
I FIGURED WHO'D MISS ONE BOX?

09:02.142 --> 09:04.342
WHAT I NEVER
COULD HAVE IMAGINED

09:04.344 --> 09:06.444
WAS THAT THAT WAS
THE LAST BOX

09:06.446 --> 09:09.114
OF TONGUE DEPRESSORS
IN THE ENTIRE HOSPITAL.

09:09.116 --> 09:10.549
I WAS SO SCARED!

09:10.551 --> 09:12.484
SO I RAN TO MY FATHER
FOR HELP.

09:12.486 --> 09:15.320
AND I DID WHAT
ANY LOVING FATHER WOULD DO.

09:15.322 --> 09:17.989
I DELETED ANY REFERENCE
TO TONGUE DEPRESSORS

09:17.991 --> 09:21.359
FROM THE INTERNET, SCARED AN
ENTIRE HOSPITAL INTO SILENCE,

09:21.361 --> 09:23.361
AND THEN
I KILLED A TEENAGER.

09:23.363 --> 09:24.863
MONSTER.

09:24.865 --> 09:26.164
AND IT WOULD
HAVE WORKED, TOO,

09:26.166 --> 09:28.600
IF IT HADN'T BEEN
FOR YOUR BIG MOUTH!

09:28.602 --> 09:30.235
NOT SO FAST, GOVERNOR.

09:30.237 --> 09:32.671
I GOT THE WHOLE THING ON TAPE.

09:32.673 --> 09:36.207
I CARRY THIS WITH ME TO
CATALOGUE MY FAVORITE CAT CALLS.

09:36.209 --> 09:37.876
MAN: Oh, Mommy!

09:37.878 --> 09:40.745
Them titties so sweet, I'm gonna
need an insulin injection.

09:40.747 --> 09:42.480
OOH, YEAH!
[ LAUGHS ]

09:42.482 --> 09:43.748
HOLD ON.

09:43.750 --> 09:45.317
MAN: Yo, gimp, I want to pop
my nuts in your ass

09:45.319 --> 09:46.985
like shells into a shotgun.

09:46.987 --> 09:48.420
THAT'S A GOOD ONE.

09:48.422 --> 09:50.622
RUTH:
And then I killed a teenager.

09:50.624 --> 09:54.392
LOOKS LIKE THE ONLY CAT
GETTING CALLED TODAY

09:54.394 --> 09:57.862
IS THIS CAT --
CALLED TO PRISON, THAT IS!

09:57.864 --> 10:00.065
NO. NO.

10:00.067 --> 10:01.866
-BYE, DAD.
-AFTERNOON, EVERYBODY.

10:01.868 --> 10:02.968
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

10:02.970 --> 10:05.203
LOLA, YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

10:05.205 --> 10:07.138
I OWE YOU.

10:07.140 --> 10:09.040
I THINK THIS IS YOURS.

10:09.042 --> 10:12.577
I'LL BET <i> YOU</i> COULD USE THAT.

10:12.579 --> 10:14.613
[ SIGHS ]

10:17.083 --> 10:18.917
[ WALKER CLATTERS ]

10:18.919 --> 10:22.621
OKAY, WHERE WERE WE?

10:22.623 --> 10:24.656
AAAH.

10:24.658 --> 10:28.827
THAT TONGUE DEPRESSOR
TASTES LIKE A DOG TRACK.

10:28.829 --> 10:30.328
[ PLAYS CHORD ]

10:30.330 --> 10:33.598
[ MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]
